Transparent, userfriendly, free and lossless [[MicroPayment]], embedded into
a [[WikiDialog]] or more generally into Social Interaction within a SocialNetwork.
Simple like a LikeButton or inserting a Link.
The next version of YourCent (the "YouTube" of MicroPayment) may be a candidate for this.

This tool will support [[SuperLiquidDemocracy]].
It will be essential for [[MicropaymentAndOlpc]].

